-- ✓ 3-method hook chain: hookmetamethod → getrawmetatable → direct remote monitoring
-- ✓ Broadened ShouldInterceptGunFire: Player gun tutuyorsa ALL FireServer intercept
-- ✓ Shared remote detection: Workspace.Remote "shoot" komutu yakalanır
-- ✓ Trigger Bot: Mobile için auto-fire, kamera crosshair'da hedef varsa ateş eder
